headline.print_headline: WWII Vet Graduates From High School 71 Years Later
headline.main: WWII Vet Graduates From High School 71 Years Later

lead_paragraph: A World War II veteran in New Mexico has gotten his high school diploma — 71 years after he was drafted and left school.
